    cli (>= 2.5.0),
    checkmate,
    readr,
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    yaml,
    withr,
    rmarkdown,
    pillar,
    rlang,
    magrittr,
    tidyselect,
    lifecycle
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
SystemRequirements: C++14
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp,
    BH
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
